    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Compared family-based skills training (aka, Behavioral Family Systems Therapy) to youth with
      poorly controlled type 1 diabetes and their parents either face-to-face or over SkypeTM.
      Examined the differential impact on the youth's adherence to the diabetes medical regimen and
      the youth's blood sugar control.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
